# Requirements Spreadsheet (Mock XLSX Content)

## User Management Requirements

### Functional Requirements

#### REQ-001: User Registration
As a new user
I want to create an account
So that I can access the system

**Acceptance Criteria**:
- Valid email required
- Password must be 8+ characters
- Confirmation email sent
- Account activated upon email verification

#### REQ-002: User Login
As a registered user
I want to log into the system
So that I can access my dashboard

**Acceptance Criteria**:
- Authentication via email/password
- Remember me option available
- Account lockout after 5 failed attempts
- Password reset functionality

#### REQ-003: Profile Management
As a logged-in user
I want to update my profile
So that my information stays current

**Acceptance Criteria**:
- Edit name, email, phone number
- Change password with current password verification
- Upload profile picture
- Save changes with confirmation

### Non-Functional Requirements

#### NFR-001: Performance
- Login response time < 2 seconds
- Profile update response time < 1 second
- Support 1000 concurrent users

#### NFR-002: Security
- All passwords hashed with bcrypt
- HTTPS required for all authentication
- Session timeout after 30 minutes inactivity
- CSRF protection on all forms

### Business Rules

#### BR-001: Password Policy
- Minimum 8 characters
- At least one uppercase letter
- At least one lowercase letter
- At least one number
- At least one special character

#### BR-002: Account Management
- Email addresses must be unique
- Usernames must be unique
- Account disabled after 90 days inactivity
- Data retention for 7 years after account deletion